hopobject.body: Would you like to leave a message? medel.com.cn Prosecutors said he shot indiscriminately, including at women and children, often from as close as a yard away. Prosecutors described gruesome scenes: A woman who was grabbed by the hair and slammed into a baby rocker. Another who had pieces of her husband's brain and skull on her hands after he was shot. An elderly woman who didn't die immediately after being shot, prompting Bales to crush her head with his boot.
